2313 2407 Last week , Hezbollah fighters killed three Israeli soldiers and seriously wounded six others .
2408 2479 The Israelis suffered a record 39 deaths in southern Lebanon last year .
2480 2590 In addition , 73 soldiers were killed en route to Lebanon when two military helicopters crashed last February .
